<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Iniciar sesión</title>
    <style>
        .social-icons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .social-icons img {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
        }
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        header, footer {
            background-color: #e0e0e0;
            padding: 20px 50px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        header nav a {
            margin-left: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
        }

        .navbar-nav .nav-item {
            margin-left: 20px;
        }

        .btn-donar {
            background-color: #3b559d;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        main {
            flex-grow: 1;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: white;
        }

        .login-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .login-container h2 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .login-container input[type="email"],
        .login-container input[type="password"] {
            width: calc(100% - 20px);
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .login-container input.invalid {
            border-color: red;
        }

        .login-container button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #3b559d;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .login-container button:hover {
            background-color: #2e4372;
        }

        .login-container a {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: gray;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .login-container p:last-child {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: gray;
        }

        .login-container p:last-child a {
            margin-left: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
        }

        .error-message {
            color: red;
            font-size: 14px;
            display: none;
        }

        footer {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        footer div {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-right: 30px;
        }

        footer div a {
            margin-top: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
    <div><img src="/static/logo.png" alt="Logo" style="max-height: 50px;"></div>
    <nav>
        <a href="#">Sobre nosotros</a>
        <a href="/mapaHeladeras">Heladeras</a>
        <a href="/elegirDonacion" class="btn-donar">Donar</a>
    </nav>
</header>

<main>
    <div class="login-container">
        <h2>Iniciar sesión</h2>
        {{#error}}
        <p class="error-message">{{error}}</p>
        {{/error}}
        <form action="/login" method="post">
            <p>Ingresa tu correo electrónico</p>
            <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="correo@dominio.com" required>
            <p>Ingresa tu contraseña</p>
            <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Ingresa tu contraseña" required>
            <button type="submit">Continuar</button>
        </form>
        <a href="/elegirRegistroCuenta" class="btn btn-primary">¿No tenés una cuenta? Crear cuenta</a>
        <p>Al hacer clic en continuar, estás aceptando nuestra <a href="#">política de privacidad y términos de uso</a>.</p>
    </div>
</main>

<footer>
    <div>
        <p><img src="/static/logo.png" alt="Logo" style="max-height: 50px;"></p>
        <div class="social-icons">
            <a href="#"><img src="/static/facebook-icon.png" alt="Facebook"></a>
            <a href="#"><img src="/static/instagram-icon.png" alt="Instagram"></a>
            <a href="#"><img src="/static/twitter-icon.png" alt="Twitter"></a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div>
        <h4>Más información</h4>
        <a href="#">Contactanos</a>
        <a href="#">Sobre nosotros</a>
        <a href="#">Sobre el proyecto</a>
    </div>
    <div>
        <h4>Donar</h4>
        <a href="#">Donar vianda</a>
        <a href="#">Ver mapa</a>
        <a href="#">Donar dinero</a>
    </div>
</footer>


</body>
</html>